During this project, we faced several challenges.

The biggest challenge was implementing SCD Type 2 correctly while maintaining historical employee records.

Another challenge was generating realistic analytical datasets and ensuring accurate relationships between fact and dimension tables.

From this project, I gained practical experience in Data Warehousing, Star Schema Design, Oracle SQL, SCD Type 2 implementation, SQL Views, and Oracle Analytics Cloud dashboard development.

